About
Carl's Jr. is located at the address 56335 Mojave Pte in Baker, California 92309.  They can be contacted via phone at (760) 733-1014 for pricing, hours and directions.  For more information go to www.carlsjr.comFor maps and directions to Carl's Jr. view the map to the right.  For reviews of Carl's Jr. see below.









