        1/7/2016
    








            Listed in TAKE OUT, YELP 100, 2016, Fast Food


What a sad turn of affairs that the amazing and iconic "Bun Boy" has been replaced by a Carl's Jr. burger. But I guess if it had to be any fast food burger to replace it - this would be a good one.Carl's Jr. offers some fairly good burgers - even at the mouth of the Mojave Desert. So if you are sick and tired of the Gyros at The Mad Greek - come here - for curly fries, a Big Carl, and a Shake.




