About:
Fast Food.Carl's Jr. was established in 1941,  in Baker, CA - San Bernardino County and  is a business listed in the categories Restaurants/Food & Dining, Full-Service Restaurants, Limited-Service Restaurants, Eating Places and Restaurants and offers Appetizers, Baked Goods & Desserts, Breakfast Foods, Burgers, Children's Menu, Dinner, Late Night, Luncheon, Open Late, Supper etc. If you did business with Carl's Jr., please leave a review and help us improve and help other people. Also, don't forget to mention Hubbiz.
          
        


Categories:

            Restaurants/Food & Dining, 
