        2/12/2012
    

I have said it before and I will say it again. I love Carl's JR burgers. I know most people prefer an InNOut but Carl's JR is where I go when I want a burger quick and conveniently. Still, I would not normally give them a 5 star review.This location is in Baker, we were here around sunset and it was eerily quiet and lots of crows. Spooky even.The reasons this one gets a 5 star review? The staff were friendly, the place was clean, the food was cooked perfectly, the burgers didnt fall apart and when I went to throw out my cup they reminded me that I could get a refill to go. They certainly went above and beyond expectations...!




