        8/27/2014
    








1 check-in
        









            Listed in You are dead to me!


Baker is fast food central.  Most the big guys are there.  The King, the Colonel, Jack, Subway, a Alien jerky operation, and some Greek guy with a mental disorder.  Where's the damn Clown?  No Clown!  I love the Clown and his Golden Arches!Then you got this place.  I had forgotten my contempt for Carl's Jr.  I was lured in by the Texas BBQ Thickburger propaganda.   False advertising!  I tried one today and it was horrible!  Took two bites and threw it in the trash.Then I bought a Crispy Chicken Sandwich with Swiss and Bacon.  Better than the Texas BBQ shit sandwich but not by much.  The salt level burned my taste buds. Thanks for the sodium.Never going to a Carl's Jr. again.








