        6/8/2017
    

Slow af, my girl ordered chicken tenders and got jalapeño poppers. When we went back inside to exchange them for the chicken tenders the guy took the jalapeño poppers put them back on the heating rack and gave her, her burnt chicken tenders. They took 10 minutes when I was the only one at the restaurant. I would not eat here again.

















