        1/1/2015
    








1 check-in
        


On the way home from Vegas, we stopped at Baker to get lunch to eat in the car.  The location was busy.  There were about 5 people ahead of us in line (one cashier), however, the line moved fairly fast.  After ordering, we got our food in about 12 minutes.  It was enough time for a bathroom break and a few sips of the fountain soda, then it was back on the road towards home.  They got my burger correct (only lettuce, tomato, and ketchup).  That doesn't always happen believe it or not!  Service was good at Carl's Jr.  I'll be back if we are in the area (to or from Vegas).Xie Xie!

















        Was this review …?
    







