        4/15/2017
    

Review for drive thru only.  Slowest drive thru ever.  Must be short staffed because they ask you to wait between each car as they assemble the prior order.  No comment as to food as I haven't received it yet but 10 minutes and 2 cars in drive thru lane is ridiculous when clearly it looks slow inside.  They should call it slow food.




